Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道他的全名吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you know his full name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不熟这孩子.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l barely knew the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,吉.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:50.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好像叫吉.\N- 詹姆斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Jim.\N- James.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:52.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,叫詹姆斯·赫尔利.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,James Hurley.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:55.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他是从双峰镇来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was from Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:58.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个流窜者.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a drifter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:03.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当玛舒太太把车停在路边时\N估计他已经流窜已久了.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was probably long gone by the time\NMr. Marsh pulled out of the driveway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:05.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他在这儿干了很长时间?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he work here long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:08.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,玛舒太太雇他\N在这儿修积架.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Marsh hired him\Nto fix the Jaguar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,积架...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaguar...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:16.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,积--架-- 一辆跑车.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-A-G-W-- A car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:17.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么碰见他的, 玛舒太太?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you meet him, Mrs. Marsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:21.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杰弗里的积架在沃里吧\N附近抛锚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeffrey's Jaguar broke down\Nnear Wallies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:24.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我跑进去借电话打.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l went in to use the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他说能帮忙.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He offered to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:31.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 我们会去查的. 谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we'll check that. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:40.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们向\N詹姆斯·赫尔利告别吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so we bid adieu\Nto James Hurley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:43.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点, 伊夫林.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, Evelyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:49.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不肯定我能容忍\N一个神经兮兮的同谋.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not sure l can tolerate\Na nervous co-conspirator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:53.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想它快点结束, 好了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just want it over with, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:57.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,都依你了, 玛舒太太.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you say, Mrs. Marsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯, 我们靠自己是\N摆不平这事的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,James, we can't get out of this\Nby ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得找人\N帮我们.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna need someone\Nto help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:28.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没干.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:31.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是马科杀了玛舒先生.\N我是被人陷害的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm killed Mr. Marsh.\Nl'm being framed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:33.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要我给你拿点什么喝吗,\N海沃德小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can l get you something,\NMiss Hayward?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不. 不, 谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看, 这没什么区别.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能干坐着\N等警察来捉我们.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't wait for the cops\Nto catch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:50.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我觉得我应该给艾德打电话.\N- 别, 别, 不要.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l think l should call Ed.\N- No, no, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:53.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我得-- 我唯一的机会\N就是亲自去和伊夫林谈谈.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l gotta-- My only chance\Nis to talk to Evelyn myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:57.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她能告诉我这是个陷阱,\N或许她也会这样和警察说的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf she told me that this was all a setup,\Nmaybe she'll just tell the police that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不来点儿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你一个机会都没有.\N警察早就在那等着你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have a chance.\NThe cops will be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得继续赶路.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:10.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她会听我的.\N我知道她会的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd listen to me though.\Nl know she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:12.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须给电话艾德.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna go call Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,留在这.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:31.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨, 艾德? 嗨, 是唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Ed? Hi, it's Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:36.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听着, 我来不及多说了,\N但詹姆斯惹麻烦了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, l don't have a lot of time,\Nbut l think James is in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 他一直在给\N一个女人打工.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's been working\Nfor this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,帮她修车,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working on her car,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:43.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后\N出了个交通事故，之后...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l think\Nthere's been this accident and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨, 好吗, 伊薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, how are you doing, Yvette?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听着, 我听说你\N你有新男友了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, l heard about\Nyour new boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:53.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊, 那太好了, 真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's great, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听到这消息真好.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么和我讲讲他的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 打搅了.\N- 海, 法兰.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Excuse me.\N- Hi, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:11.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你在雪莉家\N干什么, 波比?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing\Nat Shelly's house last night, Bobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:14.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉差点就被杀死了\N你还有心思问我在那干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly almost gets murdered and\Nyou're worried about what l'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:15.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不问问里欧那饭桶?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Leostein?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:19.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在\N雪莉家干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing\Nat Shelly's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:23.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看, 就说白了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, here's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:27.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉和我好上了, 行了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly and l are together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:30.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉死前,\N我们就在一起好一阵子了,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been for a long time,\Nsince before Laura died,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:33.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有在里欧痴呆流口水的\N之前之后都在一起.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before and after Leo\Nwent into his drool mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:34.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:38.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,锯木厂失火那晚\N你在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you\Nthe night the mill burned?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:40.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那和这有什么关系?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that got to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧要杀死你.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo tried to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:45.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你就开枪打他.\N- 不可能.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Maybe you shot him.\N- No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,木厂失火那晚\N我去找雪莉了,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l went to Shelly's\Nthe night the mill burned down,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我担心她.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because l was worried about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,汉克·詹宁斯的子弹\N穿过窗户打中他时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was about to bury an ax\Nin my head
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:53.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他差点就把斧头\N砍进我脑袋了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when Hank Jennings shot him\Nthrough the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:56.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你肯定是汉克吗?\N- 绝对是.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You sure it was Hank?\N- Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧和汉克之间有什么关系?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Hank's connection with Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道, 爷儿.\N不如你来告诉我好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know, man.\NWhy don't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:04.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉, 你觉得里欧\N现在会在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly, do you have any idea\Nwhere Leo might be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, l don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:11.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会派2个警官去你家\N一天24小时.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll assign a couple of my deputies\Nto the house 24 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 爷儿,\N我能照顾雪莉，好吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, man,\Nl can take care of Shelly all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你就省了派警官吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just save the deputies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比·布里格斯,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby Briggs,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,打住.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,button it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:22.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你现在可以走了.\N- 行.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You can go now.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:25.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉, 别担心, 我们不会\N让你离开视线范围的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly, don't worry, we're not\Ngonna let you out of our sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢你.\N- 来吧, 雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you.\N- Come on, Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得安全多了,\N是吧, 雪莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel so much safer,\Ndon't you, Shelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,悠着点, 小流氓.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a life, punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:46.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,又一趟「西雅图到\N双峰镇" 的穿梭之旅.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another trip on the ''Seattle\Nto Twin Peaks'' shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看来挺好嘛, 哈里.\N- 是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Looking good, Harry.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 艾伯特.\N- 库.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Albert.\N- Coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:56.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 先生们.\N- 你带什么来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Gentlemen.\N- What have you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:58.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来双峰镇就是为了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My invite back to Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:01.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,云顿·厄尔.\N戈登·寇尔直接命令的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windom Earle.\NDirect orders from Gordon Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正如他自己说的:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As he so succinctly put it:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"我担心库呢."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''l'm worried about Coop.''
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:17.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,斯普林菲尔德, 堪萨斯城,\N罗敦市, 达拉斯, 杰克逊.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Springfield, Kansas City,\NLawton, Dallas, Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:19.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,厄尔都已经\N给警察局和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earle's been sending\Ngift-wrapped packages
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:22.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,主要执法机关\N送过礼包了.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to police departments\Nand major law enforcement agencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:25.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,每个看起来都像是邮包炸弹,\N但最后都被证实无害.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each looks like a mail bomb,\Nbut they turn out to be harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:28.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快递员收到\N云顿·厄尔签名的假信用卡.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deliveries were paid for by a phony\Ncredit card signed Windom Earle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,盒子里是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's in the boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:33.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,每个都装着一件服饰.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One article of clothing in each.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:40.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 一条白面纱, 2, 一条吊袜带,\N3, 一双白便鞋,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, a white veil, two, a garter,\Nthree, a pair of white slippers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:45.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,4 , 一条珍珠项链,\N最后, 一套婚纱.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,four, a pearl necklace,\Nand finally, a wedding dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是凯若琳的.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caroline's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:51.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,毒监部和联邦调查局要捉他,\N更别说密西西比州, 俄克拉何马州
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got DEA and FBl,\Nnot to mention Mississippi, Oklahoma
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和伊利诺斯州的巡逻队了\N都在通缉他.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lllinois State patrols\Nlooking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都被邀请到舞会里了.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's invited to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:09:00.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我猜, 除了你，库\N他不会和任何人共舞.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my guess is, he won't dance\Nwith anyone but you, Coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:08.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,办公室的流浪汉\N死因是大动脉被切断.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vagrant from the office died\Nfrom a knife wound severing the aorta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:11.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的手指\N直指着这颗棋子.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's finger is pointed\Ndirectly at this chess piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是尸体已经僵直了\N厄尔是怎样做到这一点呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did Earle manage that\Nwith the rigor mortis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 新死的人是从头开始\N慢慢僵硬之脚趾.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, rigor mortis goes\Nfrom head to toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但2天之后,\N僵直会从脚趾向头部逆行一次.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after two days,\Nit leaves the body from toe to head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:21.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么他就等逆行，\N至手臂手指处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he waited for it to leave\Nthe arms and the fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:25.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再将它们指向\N棋盘上.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they could be maneuvered\Nonto the chess board.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:28.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后又装神弄鬼\N把发电站炸个底朝天.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then he played Zeus\Nat the power station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:31.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 发现什么了?\N- 就这地图.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What was found?\N- This map.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,粘在桌子底下.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taped to the bottom of a table.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:36.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,干的好, 艾伯特.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问.\N他已经开始行动了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's making his move.\NMost definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:49.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}是啊.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:56.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 库, 你这身打扮.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Coop, about the uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:57.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了, 艾伯特?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Albert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:10:00.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,比起你那套优雅的\N黑西服加领带
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Replacing the quiet elegance\Nof the dark suit and tie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这身土里巴叽的\N泥色便服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the casual indifference\Nof these muted earth tones
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:07.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是自毁潮流,\N不过我也疯了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a form of fashion suicide,\Nbut call me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来穿在你身上, 还行.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On you, it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 艾伯特.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈，你醒了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:54.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,想必你睡的很香吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l trust you've slept well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:59.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你睡着的时候,\N我已经全部了解你过了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you've slept,\Nl've learned all about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:02.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧·强生.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:06.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,警察可想尽快\N见到你呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police would like to see you\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:09.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 让我来看看.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:12.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,走私毒品.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drug trafficking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纵火.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:18.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谋杀未遂.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attempted murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:24.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,家庭暴力.\N我喜欢这部分.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Domestic violence.\NNow l am partial to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 里欧, 我已经清洗过你的伤口.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Leo, l've cleansed your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the mend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:33.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经除去了\N你的肉中刺.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've removed the proverbial thorn\Nfrom your paw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:37.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧. 里欧是狮子王.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo. Leo the lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:41.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:44.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你帮助我.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和服从我.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:48.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会照办吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:54.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗,\N在13世纪的日本,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that,\Nin the 1 3th century in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:57.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,武士被剥夺了\N他们的武器之后.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the samurai were stripped\Nof their weaponry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:01.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们却发现常年\N佩戴在身的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:12:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they discovered that the aged\Nand treated bamboo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:07.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尺八长笛\N可以当作出色的短棒来使用.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of their shakuhachi flute\Nmade an excellent cudgel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:14.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这长笛\N真实个令人愉快的好乐器啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This flute\Nis truly an instrument of pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:24.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这项链我本想留着\N合适场合才用,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanted to save this necklace\Nfor an occasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:27.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但你破坏气氛了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you've ruined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:34.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,过来这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:41.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你煮了些稀粥.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've made you some gruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:52.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,过来, 里欧, 来吃你的稀粥.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Leo, eat your gruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:55.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好滋味, 香喷喷.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum, yum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:08.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一转眼20年了, 宝贝儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's been 20 years, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,毕业舞会\N似乎还是昨日之事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day we're talking\Nabout a graduation party
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:14.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而如今我们却已在这了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the next day we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:19.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除了无尽感伤\N就什么都没有了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in between\Nnothing but a world of hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我尽量不去想它.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l tried not to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我把时间越来越多\N放在餐馆的生意上,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just spent\Nmore and more time at the diner,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:35.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,努力让它好好运作起来.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to make the place work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为除此之外，我就一无所有了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because l had nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们每天如常开门,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were open every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:45.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就不会想去过\N另一种生活了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so l wouldn't have to have\Nanother life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不过生日,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No birthdays,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:51.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不过国庆,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no Fourth of July,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也不过圣诞.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:14:03.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 我把我所有的圣诞节\N都变成工作日.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l turned all my Christmases\Ninto a week full of Mondays.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当这样也不起作用时,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that didn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:11.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就开始想那些礼物\N那些我从没给你买过.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought about all the presents\Nl never bought you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:14.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也从来没送过你的礼物.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never got to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:20.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我去年给你\N买了圣诞礼物.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l bought you a present\Nlast Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:25.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是一条绿宝石镶嵌玛瑙的饰扣宝路领带.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was a turquoise and onyx bolo tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:29.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我走到你家门前\N想把它送给你,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l walked over to your house\Nto give it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:34.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我没敢进去.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but l couldn't go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是默默等着.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:39.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看着你在窗前走过.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l could see you through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:43.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我为什么没敢进去.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know why l couldn't go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我没做到.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry l didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我常想,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:59.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在我家里的，在我床上的.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should have been in my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本应该是你.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:07.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是将来, 艾德.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's about the future now, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:10.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和我们的将来要做点什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what we're gonna do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:16.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚，我餐厅关门后\N我想你来接我.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to come tonight\Nafter l close the diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:18.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,接我回家.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是对的.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:22.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,未来就在我们前方.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's all ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有的是时间.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:28.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小艾艾?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 小艾艾?\N- 不, 不, 不.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Eddie?\N- No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:33.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是现在和她谈谈好.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l may as well talk to her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:49.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好, 纳丁.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Nadine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:53.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在刀河\N一路杀进区决赛,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got all the way\Nto the district finals at Knife River,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:58.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,却只为了\N空中灌篮是违规的.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only to find out\Nthe airplane slam is illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:03.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就这样被取消资格了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:06.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第二名, 真讨厌.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second place, what a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 好小子, 有够倒霉的, 哼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy, what a tough break, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好, 纳丁.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Nadine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l owe you an apology, Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:18.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我得向你道歉, 诺玛.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:22.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说, 我真是把汉克揍惨了这次\N很对不起.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, l really pounded Hank\Nand l am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:26.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为当时我以为\N他真会伤到小艾艾.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l thought he was gonna do\Nsomething to Eddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:30.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就抓狂了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l sort of got mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:43.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know about you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的事我都知道了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的, 真的没问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's really, really okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样我就不会为\N我和迈克的事感到太内疚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because l don't have to feel so guilty\Nabout me and Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:54.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你和迈克?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:56.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想陷进去的,\N但我不得不告诉你,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't wanna get into it,\Nbut l have to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:17:00.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是非常, 非常认真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:17:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is really, really serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you guys can go ahead\Nand do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:04.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你们该干什么\N就干什么去吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:09.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我对此已经\N完全没感觉了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am completely cool\Nabout all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:33.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:41.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,西雅图警方想要答案\N我得告诉他们点什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seattle police want answers\Nand l have to tell them something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们知道你和乔纳森\N有关系.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They know you were connected\Nwith Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:47.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么死的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:50.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他后脑\N中了3枪.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was shot three times\Nin the back of the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:56.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你以前从未说过真相,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you were ever gonna tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:04.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就是个最佳时机了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now would be an ideal time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想得再来一杯咖啡了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think l'll get another cup of joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗, 皮特?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that you, Pete?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:27.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是我. 库珀?\N- 在.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah. Cooper?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:31.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,终于从一大堆杂活里脱开身了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l get over to the Clean and Save
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:35.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼·帕勃列\N还在柜台那边忙着呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Jeanie Pombelek\Nis working the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She does not speak\None word of English.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:38.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她连一句英语\N都不会说.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:41.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个词都不会, 上了拉链似的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nada, zip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她是从布达佩斯来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's from Budapest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就站在那儿\N你眼看我眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just stood there\Nand looked at each other
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,像木头人一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like we were made of wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:50.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些衣服是谁的, 皮特?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who does all this belong to, Pete?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:55.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳把她使唤来\N使唤去，快把她累死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine's been running her\Ninto the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 要帮忙?\N- 所以我就贡献点力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Need a hand?\N- So l offered to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:19:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the dry cleaners\Nand pick up Josie's stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:01.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,中途停个便车\N去帮乔西拿点东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:06.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道么, 匈牙利语\N我只会2个词，红辣椒和菜炖牛肉.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the only words l know\Nin Hungarian are paprika and goulash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt took me 20 minutes\Nto get this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:09.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我先去放好这些东西\N就20分钟.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我来接. 来帮个手.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get that. Give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:17.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:24.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 找乔西的. 她在吗?\N- 她在另一间房, 皮特.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lt's for Josie. ls she here?\N- She's in the other room, Pete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello.\N- Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:48.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 你好.\N- 乔西.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我是托马斯.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:53.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我真高兴终于找到你了.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so glad l've found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:57.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前一直在想\N我们还能再续前缘吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was wondering\Nif we could get together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:02.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道\N乔纳森发生什么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear about\Nwhat happened to Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}可怕吧.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}可怕吧.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:10.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎到双峰镇,\N埃卡先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Twin Peaks,\NMr. Eckhardt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:20.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她又回到凯萨琳·马爹利身边了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's run back to Catherine Martell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我很失望.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So l asked Stonewall Jackson\Nwhat he would like to do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:33.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,于是，我就问史东沃·杰克逊\N在我们把那些北佬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,赶到加拿大去之后\N他最想干什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after we run the Yankees\Nup to Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said: ''Follow them.\Nl wanna be the Duke of Montreal.''
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:40.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他说，跟他们一样.\N我要做蒙特利尔公爵."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that Stonewall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:45.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 那个史东沃.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l once asked him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:46.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有一次我问他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:49.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得我应该\N跟林肯干吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what he thought\Nl should do with Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he says, ''Old Honest Abe\Nis about as useful to you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:53.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他就说, "那个老实巴交的亚伯\N对你来说，
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a spittoon cleaner\Nin a whorehouse.''
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:58.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,充其量不过是个\N妓院的床底尿壶罢了."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,旅行者，稳住了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:07.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看, 杰柯比医生?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Dr. Jacoby?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:10.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,带他出来逛\N看来也没什么帮助.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting him out to mingle with the\Npublic doesn't seem to have helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 但你得承认,\N他在这倒玩的挺开心的.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you have to admit,\Nhe's kind of fun this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:16.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你也犯病了?\N那可是我爸, 你哥呀.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you?\NThat's my father, your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:19.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能由他这样.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now, Audrey, honey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:21.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 现在, 欧蕊, 小甜甜, 听我说.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some advantages\Nto leaving him...insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:26.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,由他这样疯\N还是有点好处的.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--told me that every man,\Nwoman and child...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:30.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,--告诉我所有男人,\N女人和小孩的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Audrey,\Nyou know l was upset too,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:32.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 欧蕊,\N你知道我也心烦,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's some projects,\Nboth domestic and international,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:36.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在我或许有机会,\N去发展一些,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:38.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,国内和国际\N业务了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that l'd might get a chance\Nto develop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, one man's crisis\Nis another man's opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:42.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说, 一鸡死\N一鸡鸣.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:44.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你些事,\N杰里叔叔.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something,\NUncle Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:49.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们由他这样的话,\N那我就变成财产遗属执行人了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We leave him the way he is,\Nand l become executor of the estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, it's a little more complicated\Nthan that, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:52.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 这事可没那么\N简单, 甜心.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:55.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 就这么简单.\N我会验收他的遗属, 杰里.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't.\Nl've examined his will, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:22:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf my father becomes incapacitated,\Nit all goes to me when l'm old enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:22:00.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我父亲不能再胜任了,\N等我到了法定年龄，一切都归我所有.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:05.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚好够年龄了, 杰,\N而他也刚好不能再胜任了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l am old enough, Jer,\Nand he is incapacitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have my way either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:08.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样，我有自己的做事方式.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the only project\Nyou'll be developing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:11.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当你唯一能发展的\N项目就是在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is selling baseboard heaters\Nat the local Cash 'n' Carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:15.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当地买现卖期交易所\N推销挂壁暖气时 .
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened to the man\Nis a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.93,0:22:20.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那堪称\N一个男人的悲剧.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:23.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是一个悲剧, 杰.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt is a tragedy, Jer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Jacoby,\Nl want you to bring my father back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:32.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杰柯比医生,\N我要你把我爸爸带回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.89,0:22:35.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 会办公室吗?\N- 列队, 稍息!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.90,0:22:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- To the office?\N- Parade, rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:37.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,回现实世界.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think it's time we implement\Nthe Appomattox scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:43.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是时候执行\N阿波马托克斯方案了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:47.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 抱歉我来晚了. 2个机车党\N想抢我这外套.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, sorry l'm late. A couple of bikers\Ntried to take this jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:49.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但老史东沃\N现在已离我而去,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But old Stonewall's\Ngone from me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cut down in a hail of Yankee lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:52.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在北佬的一片欢呼声中被杀死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.11,0:22:54.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他独自死去,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:57.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有我的抚慰.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without my comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:22:58.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,拉蒂.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:22:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:01.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,过来这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what l wanna hear.\NTroops, about face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:05.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知我想听到什么.\N部队, 向后转.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:07.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"南方州际." "南方州际"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Dixie.'' ''Dixie''!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward, march.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:10.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,向前, 起步走.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l wish l was in the land of cotton
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:15.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}噢, 我愿此刻身在棉花地里{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:18.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}过往美好日子永不忘怀{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.47,0:23:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old times there were not forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.68,0:23:25.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}放眼远方, 放眼远方, 放眼远方\N南方州际{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.68,0:23:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look away, look away, look away\NDixie land
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:26.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}噢, 我多希望...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:46.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,玛舒太太?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Marsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:50.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是唐娜, 詹姆斯的朋友.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.47,0:23:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Donna, James' friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.88,0:23:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:55.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我认得你.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:23:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the lady here a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.72,0:23:57.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给这位小姐来杯饮料.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:24:00.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要带小伞装饰的.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:24:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a little umbrella in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, dear, sit down, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.94,0:24:02.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,继续吧, 亲爱的, 来坐下, 放松点.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:06.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你为什么要这样对詹姆斯?\N- 那为什么不?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why are you doing this to James?\N- Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.23,0:24:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:07.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是个好人.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.19,0:24:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was good at two things:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.20,0:24:11.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他对2样东西都好:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:13.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,车和我.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.13,0:24:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you?\Nl'm talking about our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:17.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你还不懂, 是吧?\N我现在讲的是我们的生活.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,0:24:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life. Life will be rosy if you can\Njust get out of one silly little jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.55,0:24:23.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,生活. 生活是美好的\N道路是曲折的.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.77,0:24:25.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.78,0:24:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.54,0:24:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.55,0:24:27.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也许不是.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.77,0:24:29.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,几年后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.78,0:24:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me in a couple of years
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:31.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,等你的生活遭的一坨屎一样\N你再来和我讲人生大道理吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.21,0:24:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when your whole life\Nhas turned to crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.81,0:24:34.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你非得要把每件事搞得毫无意义\N或者愚蠢至极，你才安心是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.82,0:24:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like to make everything\Nsound pointless and stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.65,0:24:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf there was a reason to climb out\Nof this primeval swill,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.68,0:24:38.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这世上有一个理由\N能从这肮脏混世中爬上来,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.92,0:24:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,believe me, dear, l'd know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.94,0:24:41.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我, 亲爱的, 我早就上岸了.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.63,0:24:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.64,0:24:42.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会么, 你真的会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.13,0:24:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here we are.\NThe car's waiting, Mrs. Marsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:47.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 我们该走了.\N车子在等着呢, 玛舒太太.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.83,0:24:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.86,0:24:49.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,上车去吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.28,0:24:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry about your friend, honey.\NThere's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.29,0:24:59.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我为你朋友的事感到很难过, 小蜜糖.\N你帮不上什么的.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.15,0:25:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you trundle along\Nto your little town,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.16,0:25:03.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，你为什么不自个儿乖乖\N滚回你的那个小镇,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.82,0:25:08.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道那儿安全多了,\N如果再让我看到你,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.82,0:25:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,safe in the knowledge that,\Nif l ever see you here again,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.35,0:25:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.38,0:25:11.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会杀了你.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.99,0:25:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this to him, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.99,0:25:17.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别那样对他, 求你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.76,0:25:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.77,0:25:19.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.77,0:25:36.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库, 看一下这个.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.78,0:25:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.18,0:25:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vicuna thread sample\Ntaken from Josie's coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.21,0:25:39.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西大衣上取的\N骆马毛线的样本.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.15,0:25:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traces found on the floor\Noutside your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.17,0:25:42.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你房间外地板上\N找到的毛线.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.96,0:25:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're from the same coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.99,0:25:44.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它们来自同一件大衣上?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.96,0:25:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me put it to you this way,\Neither Josie Packard pulled the trigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.99,0:25:47.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让我这样跟你说吧,\N要不就是乔西·帕卡开的枪,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.99,0:25:50.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要不就是她把她的冬衣\N错借给坏人穿了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.99,0:25:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or she's loaning her winter wear\Nto the wrong people.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.33,0:25:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lt's a perfect match.\N- What about the gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.34,0:25:52.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 完全吻合.\N- 那手套呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.40,0:25:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Checking for powder burns.\Nl'll have the results in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.43,0:25:54.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正在检测弹药伤痕.\N我早上就会拿到结果.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.17,0:25:56.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是西雅图的凶案?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.17,0:25:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the Seattle Homicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.40,0:25:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Locals are looking\Nfor a beautiful Asian woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.43,0:25:58.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当局正在找\N一名美丽的亚洲女人,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.87,0:26:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,late 20s, in connection with the murder\Nof one Jonathan Kumagai.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.91,0:26:02.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,约二十七、八岁, 乔纳森·曲末该谋杀案\N嫌疑人 .
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.31,0:26:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has an lnterpol sheet\Nas long as your arm
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.34,0:26:04.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,曲末该先生的跨国犯案表\N有你的手臂那么长
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.61,0:26:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and three holes\Nin the back of his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.65,0:26:06.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有3个洞\N在他后脑勺.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.15,0:26:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm betting the bullets will match\Nthe slugs we took from your vest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.17,0:26:10.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我敢断定子弹和你背心上\N取下来的弹片相符合.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.35,0:26:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope it's not Josie,\Nfor Harry's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.39,0:26:14.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望不是乔西,\N为了哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.89,0:26:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop, as you know, Truman and l\Nhave had our differences in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.91,0:26:19.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库, 你也知道, 杜鲁门和我\N有着不同的过去.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.86,0:26:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the big lug's got his heart\Nin the right place, if nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.86,0:26:23.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但如无意外的话，他的好心肠\N给人利用了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.33,0:26:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l'm not above feeling a little\Nsympathy for the stalwart and the dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.34,0:26:26.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我丝毫感觉不到那家伙\N对这高大呆有一点怜悯之心.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.63,0:26:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's you point, Albert?\N- Speaking frankly?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.65,0:26:28.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你想说什么, 艾伯特?\N- 说实话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.67,0:26:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.69,0:26:30.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,说吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.73,0:26:34.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的紧张和她女友\N麻烦大了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.74,0:26:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our sheriff's got a serious problem\Nwith his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.75,0:26:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albert,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.78,0:26:41.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾伯特,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.58,0:26:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not one word until we're certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.61,0:26:44.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们确证之前一个字也别乱说.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.02,0:26:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.04,0:26:51.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.36,0:26:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our John Doe's got a name:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.39,0:26:54.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的约翰·豆找到一个名字:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.66,0:26:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erik Powell. Transient.\NFormer merchant marine by his prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.69,0:26:58.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,埃里·鲍尔. 暂住人员.\N这上面说他是前商船的.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.60,0:27:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Powell?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.61,0:27:00.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.03,0:27:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.04,0:27:02.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊, 想起什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.97,0:27:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Powell was Caroline's\Nmaiden name.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.00,0:27:06.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍尔是凯若琳\N女佣的名字.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.67,0:27:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think\Nthis Powell is a relative?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.69,0:27:11.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得\N这个鲍尔是亲戚吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.71,0:27:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Earle's playing the game\Naccording to his own rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.74,0:27:15.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不. 厄尔有他自己\N的游戏规则.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.55,0:27:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every move he makes\Nsends a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.56,0:27:18.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他每个举措\N都是在发出信息.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.32,0:27:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that he chose\Nthe name Powell
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.35,0:27:19.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上，是他故意选了\N一个叫鲍尔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.99,0:27:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tells me he hasn't forgotten a thing\Nthat went on between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.00,0:27:22.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他在告诉我，他一直\N没有忘记我们之间的恩怨.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.96,0:27:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So whenever he takes a piece\Nfrom the board...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.00,0:27:26.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，每当他从棋盘上\N走出一步...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.89,0:27:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.91,0:27:29.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就有人要死.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.96,0:27:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l never beat him, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.00,0:27:33.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没打败过他, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.33,0:27:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop, if you've got a need\Nfor a chess expert,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.35,0:27:35.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库, 如果你需要一个\N下棋高手,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.90,0:27:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've got one of the best\Nright here in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.91,0:27:38.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们镇上正\N有个最好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.21,0:27:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.22,0:27:41.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,将军.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.01,0:27:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.04,0:27:45.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,将军.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.41,0:27:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.44,0:27:49.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再将.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.99,0:27:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, l am impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.00,0:27:55.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,坦白说, 我服了.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.09,0:28:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l owe it all\Nto the great Jose Raul Capablanca.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.13,0:28:00.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这都得归功于\N象棋大师何西·楼·卡柏布兰卡.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.49,0:28:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if there's chess boards\Nin heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.52,0:28:02.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,此刻, 如果天堂\N也有棋盘,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.00,0:28:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jose's sitting next to the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.00,0:28:05.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,何西一定就坐在主的对面.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.50,0:28:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Doc?\N- The mind reels.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.52,0:28:08.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 医圣?\N- 脑袋都转成团了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.80,0:28:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.83,0:28:11.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.24,0:28:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pete, l need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.26,0:28:13.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,皮特, 我需要你帮助.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.84,0:28:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm playing a chess match\Nof considerable importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.87,0:28:16.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我正进行着一场\N相当重要的象棋竞赛.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.31,0:28:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't say any more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.35,0:28:17.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法透露更多.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.74,0:28:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suffice to say,\Nl'd like to stalemate the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.79,0:28:20.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只能说,\N我宁愿僵持着,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.85,0:28:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,losing as few pieces as possible.\NNone, if that can be arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.87,0:28:25.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能减少损失.\N或不损失, 如果能重整棋局.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.45,0:28:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Agent Cooper,\Nl'd be proud to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.48,0:28:30.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 库珀探员,\N我很荣幸有用武之地.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.46,0:28:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Pete.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.48,0:28:32.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢, 皮特.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.46,0:28:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great players are either far or few.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.48,0:28:36.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伟大的棋手少之又少啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.84,0:28:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi.\N- Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.87,0:28:51.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨.\N- 雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.28,0:28:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.31,0:28:53.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了那些事，我真难过.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.65,0:28:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.66,0:28:55.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.52,0:28:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.53,0:28:58.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不怎么的.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.18,0:29:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanted to come right over,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.22,0:29:00.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来过去看你的,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.69,0:29:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but with Hank gone,\Nit's been a madhouse here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.70,0:29:04.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但汉克不在之后,\N这里简直成了疯人院.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.82,0:29:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need any help, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.83,0:29:08.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要帮手了, 是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.16,0:29:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l... l'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.18,0:29:12.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我... 我想...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.70,0:29:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd feel safer, Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.75,0:29:15.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得安全多了, 诺玛.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.07,0:29:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.09,0:29:18.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是开玩笑吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.57,0:29:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt hasn't been the same without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.62,0:29:20.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿没有你，完全不同.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.91,0:29:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When can you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.92,0:29:22.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你几时能开始?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.91,0:29:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Now?\N- Great. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.92,0:29:29.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 现在啊?\N- 太好了. 欢迎回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.58,0:29:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.62,0:29:31.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.72,0:29:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Norma?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.75,0:29:32.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,诺玛?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.95,0:29:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi, Shelly.\N- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.96,0:29:34.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨, 雪莉.\N- 嗨.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.39,0:29:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.\Nl need to talk to you for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.40,0:29:38.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了.\N我要和你谈几分钟.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.23,0:29:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.27,0:29:47.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事你应该要知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.97,0:29:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hank's nearly ready\Nto leave the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.01,0:29:50.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,汉克快准备\N出院了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.10,0:29:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about his parole violations?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.14,0:29:53.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是触犯假释条例了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.91,0:29:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, this time\Nl don't want him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.92,0:29:56.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 这次\N我不想他回来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.34,0:30:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He won't be back.\NHank's going to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.36,0:30:00.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心. 他不会回来了.\N汉克要蹲大牢了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.41,0:30:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're charging him with\Nthe attempted murder of Leo Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.44,0:30:02.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正准备起诉他\N企图谋杀里欧·强生.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.98,0:30:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add that to breaking parole,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.01,0:30:05.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加上违反假释条例,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.38,0:30:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hank's going away for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.40,0:30:08.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,汉克会离开好长一段时间了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.29,0:30:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.31,0:30:11.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.38,0:30:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Eckhardt, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.40,0:30:36.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,埃卡先生, 欢迎光临.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.48,0:30:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie, help our guest with his coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.53,0:30:39.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西, 帮客人脱大衣啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.53,0:30:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l must confess l received\Nyour invitation with some surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.58,0:30:50.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得承认\N接到你的邀请有点吃惊.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.03,0:30:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, word travels fast\Nin Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.06,0:30:53.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 消息在双峰镇\N传的可快了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.00,0:30:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought it was fitting that l dined\Nwith my late brother's business rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.06,0:30:57.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想请我已故兄长的生意对手\N共进晚餐，是合礼节的.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.97,0:30:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some wine, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.01,0:30:59.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来点酒, 乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.60,0:31:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother was not always my rival.\NWe were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.62,0:31:02.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥生前也不单是我的竞争对手.\N我们也曾经是朋友.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.27,0:31:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- But your friendship soured.\N- Sadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.32,0:31:04.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但你们的友谊变质了.\N- 可悲啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.91,0:31:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men of business frequently find\Ntheir personal lives disrupted
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.93,0:31:08.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,生意人常常会发现\N他们的私生活被自己
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.31,0:31:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the larger portraits they paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.36,0:31:10.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所画的那幅巨大肖像扰乱了.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.48,0:31:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You consider yourself an artist?\NThe wine, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.54,0:31:13.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你把自己看作一个艺术家?\N酒, 乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.85,0:31:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of a sort. Your brother was as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.88,0:31:17.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧. 你哥哥也算是.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.96,0:31:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder, Mr. Eckhardt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.01,0:31:19.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道, 埃卡先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.72,0:31:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you had him killed,\Nwas it for art or money?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.75,0:31:23.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但你设计杀他时,\N到底是为了艺术还是钱呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.63,0:31:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't stand there, Josie, pour.\N- Call me Thomas. Your brother did.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.67,0:31:27.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别光站着, 乔西, 倒酒.\N- 叫我托马斯吧. 你哥哥就这样叫的.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.30,0:31:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thomas. We'll have\Nour hors d'oeuvres now, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.32,0:31:30.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,托马斯. 现在上\N开胃小菜吧，乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.54,0:31:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One does not kill for art or money.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.58,0:31:32.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人不为艺术或钱而杀人.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.80,0:31:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are commodities easily lost\Nand just as easily gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.84,0:31:36.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西来得容易去得快\N无非是些过眼云烟罢了.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.51,0:31:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, one, rather l,\Nmight find reason to kill for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.54,0:31:42.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然而, 一个人, 就说我吧,\N却有可能为爱而杀.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.05,0:31:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you love her that much?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.10,0:31:46.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你那么爱她吗?\N- 是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.09,0:31:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie has the most\Nincredible hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.10,0:31:49.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西有一双\N不可思议的美手.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.89,0:31:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every finger a thing of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.93,0:31:51.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,每一根手指都赏心悦目.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.09,0:31:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.15,0:31:54.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.96,0:32:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder,\Nwhat shall we do about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.02,0:32:01.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想,\N我们要怎么处理她呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.07,0:32:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt would be a shame\Nif you left empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.10,0:32:05.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果让你空手而回\N那多不好意思啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.47,0:32:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course,\Nl'll miss her cheery disposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.50,0:32:10.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当然,我会想念她那\N让人快乐的性情.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.38,0:32:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've become the best of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.41,0:32:12.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾经做过好朋友.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.98,0:32:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two girls chatting over tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.02,0:32:14.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,两个女孩喝茶聊天.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.05,0:32:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you should purchase\Nan animal of some kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.11,0:32:17.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许你该买只\N动物，或一只其它什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.85,0:32:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat or a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.89,0:32:19.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,猫啊狗啊之类.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.38,0:32:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf l give her to you,\Nwhat will you give me in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.41,0:32:22.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我把她给你了,\N你将会用什么回报我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.85,0:32:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can l place a value\Non something so precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.89,0:32:26.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如此珍贵的东西\N我又怎么能用价值去衡量呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.49,0:32:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you will try?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.54,0:32:33.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但你会尝试?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.23,0:32:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.28,0:32:35.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.64,0:32:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.67,0:32:39.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.40,0:32:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thomas and l\Nwill have our main course now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.46,0:32:43.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,托马斯和我\N现在准备要吃主菜了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.54,0:33:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.59,0:33:16.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要这样做?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.45,0:33:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know l've been going through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.50,0:33:23.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我深受其害的.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.75,0:33:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l can't figure it out.\N- James, you're not safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.81,0:33:26.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我解决不了.\N- 詹姆斯, 你在这不安全.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.65,0:33:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lf Malcolm finds you--\N- ls it the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.72,0:33:29.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 如果马科发现你--\N- 为了钱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.45,0:33:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that it? No. No, l got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.50,0:33:31.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗? 不. 不, 我明白了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.09,0:33:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was Malcolm. Oh, yeah.\NHe made you do it. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.15,0:33:36.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是马科. 哦, 对了.\N是他让你这样干的. 对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.66,0:33:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better tell me a story, Evelyn.\NBecause l'm all mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.72,0:33:40.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好把故事给我编好点, 伊夫林.\N因为我全糊涂了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.63,0:33:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just wanna know\Nwhy you would do this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.68,0:33:42.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想知道\N你为什么要这样对我.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.63,0:33:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,James.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.68,0:33:44.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.64,0:33:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you expect? An apology?\NA hidden heart of gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.68,0:33:51.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能期待什么呢? 一个道歉?\N一颗金子般的心?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.44,0:33:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l did it all, James. l did everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.50,0:33:54.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我做的, 詹姆斯. 所有事都是我做的.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.35,0:33:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l found you, l lured you in\Nand l kept you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.37,0:33:58.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当时，马科正设计着\N一个完美无缺的小陷阱.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.65,0:34:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while Malcolm planned\Na nice, neat little frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.68,0:34:02.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是我发现了你, 引诱你进来\N还把你留在了这儿,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.69,0:34:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why?\N- For the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.72,0:34:06.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么?\N- 为了钱.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.89,0:34:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.94,0:34:08.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,出于恐惧.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.79,0:34:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because l wanted to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.85,0:34:11.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因此我想这样做.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.83,0:34:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not exactly what you wanted\Nto hear, is it, James?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.90,0:34:15.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是你想要听到的\N是吧, 詹姆斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.53,0:34:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth hurts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.59,0:34:18.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真相很伤人吧, 不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.17,0:34:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,James, you're good\Nand you're honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.20,0:34:25.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯, 你是个\N诚实的好人.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.24,0:34:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.29,0:34:27.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.55,0:34:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean\Nthere weren't moments
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.59,0:34:29.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但不代表\N我想你留下来那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.41,0:34:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when l truly wanted you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.46,0:34:32.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.98,0:34:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for Malcolm,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.03,0:34:35.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不为马科,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.35,0:34:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or for the money, but for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.42,0:34:38.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也不为钱, 只为我.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.49,0:34:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the good and honest way\Nthat you taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.55,0:34:43.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为了尝到你的好\N你的诚实.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.93,0:34:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l like how you taste too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.99,0:34:48.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢你品尝.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.04,0:34:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm, what did you do?\NJames, James. You hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.07,0:34:57.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马科, 你干什么?\N詹姆斯, 詹姆斯. 你打伤他了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.75,0:35:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He broke into the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.81,0:35:05.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他破门而入,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.28,0:35:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was angry, he was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.33,0:35:08.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他发怒, 他抓狂.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.52,0:35:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed Jeffrey\Nand he came back to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.55,0:35:13.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了杰弗里\N现在又回来杀你.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.96,0:35:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor, defenseless little widow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.03,0:35:16.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是可怜的, 毫无防备的小寡妇.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.43,0:35:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were ready for him, Evelyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.47,0:35:19.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但你早知他会回来的, 伊夫林.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.66,0:35:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got your gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.73,0:35:21.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你准备了你的手枪,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.97,0:35:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you shot James.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.03,0:35:24.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你开枪打了詹姆斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.74,0:35:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shot him until he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.77,0:35:27.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直开枪直到打死了他.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.61,0:36:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- General Lee.\N- Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.64,0:36:05.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 李将军.\N- 喔.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.71,0:36:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to our humble horse--\NHome, General Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.78,0:36:12.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临寒马--\N寒舍, 李将军.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.35,0:36:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you. And you are...?\N- Scarlett McLean.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.43,0:36:16.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢你. 你是...?\N- 史佳丽·麦琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.22,0:36:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is my father--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.30,0:36:18.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我爸爸--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.26,0:36:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.30,0:36:21.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.66,0:36:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wilmer McLean at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.73,0:36:25.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,威尔默·麦琳随时听候你的差遣.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.76,0:36:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm indeed honored to be making\Nyour extremely sociable acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.82,0:36:28.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的非常荣幸能\N如此亲近友好的与你结交.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.97,0:36:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you armed\Nwith my sword, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.04,0:36:32.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿着我的剑\N干什么, 先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.80,0:36:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l like your sword, sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.86,0:36:35.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你的剑, 陛下.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.31,0:36:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you, Daddy. Thank you.\N- Where is General Grant?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.38,0:36:38.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢你, 爸爸. 谢谢你.\N- 格兰将军呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.11,0:36:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Grant's a-coming, sire,\Nl know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.17,0:36:41.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,格兰将军正来呢, 陛下,\N我知道的.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.75,0:36:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.82,0:36:43.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.66,0:36:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Grant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.73,0:36:55.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,格兰将军.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.99,0:36:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.04,0:36:57.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,李将军.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.80,0:37:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, we met during the Mexican War.\NDo you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.86,0:37:01.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先生, 我们是在墨西哥战争中相遇的.\N你还记得吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.50,0:37:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have come to surrender the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.56,0:37:03.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是来投降，并交出北方的.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.04,0:37:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mexican War, sir.\NDo you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.08,0:37:06.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥战争, 先生.\N你还记得吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.37,0:37:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, yes.\Nlt was a good war, as l remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.43,0:37:09.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 记得, 记得.\N我记得那是场漂亮仗.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.54,0:37:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense.\NAll wars are nothing but madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.61,0:37:13.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道.\N所有战争除了愚蠢疯狂之外，一无是处.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.18,0:37:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disguised as the patriotic ventures\Nof politicians,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.26,0:37:17.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是政客们打着爱国主义旗号\N去投机倒把的假面而已,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.48,0:37:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,too old and too cowardly\Nto participate in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.56,0:37:20.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太老太懦弱\N以至于他们不能参与其中.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.09,0:37:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No, no, sir, l have no love for war.\N- Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.17,0:37:24.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不, 不, 先生, 我对战争没有任何感情.\N- 我也没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.16,0:37:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And even less for politicians.\N- Hey, amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.21,0:37:26.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 甚至比政客们还少.\N- 嘿, 阿门.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.69,0:37:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as for the men who fight them,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.74,0:37:30.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但, 对于英勇作战的战士们,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.50,0:37:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they have my eternal respect\Nand sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.56,0:37:35.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们值得我永垂不朽的尊敬\N和哀悼.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.00,0:37:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, general,\Nenough of this fruitless conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.08,0:37:40.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 将军,\N这没完没了的对话够了.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.87,0:37:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My terms:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.95,0:37:43.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,用我的话说:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.34,0:37:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Federal officers\Nmay keep their sidearms
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.39,0:37:46.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,联邦官员们\N可以保留他们的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.61,0:37:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and other general possessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.69,0:37:49.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和其他将军的财产.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.58,0:37:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Officers and men claiming to own\Ntheir own horses may keep them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.65,0:37:53.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,军官们和士兵们可以去\N认领自己的马，并留着它们自用.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.62,0:37:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And officers and men will be allowed\Nto return to their home,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.70,0:37:58.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,军官们和士兵们\N可以回自己老家了,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.72,0:38:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not to be disturbed\Nby the Confederate States' authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.78,0:38:02.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不会被邦联当局\N骚扰了.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.89,0:38:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l surrender.\N- Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.95,0:38:05.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我投降了.\N- 你当然了.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.43,0:38:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The articles.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.48,0:38:08.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,条约.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.47,0:38:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Here, sire, the articles.\N- Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.52,0:38:13.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 在这儿, 陛下, 条约.\N- 先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.77,0:38:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The articles, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.83,0:38:16.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,条约, 先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.08,0:38:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You will sign, General Grant.\N-Oh, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.13,0:38:20.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你会签吧, 格兰将军.\N-哦, 会签, 会签, 当然了.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.28,0:38:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And may l add that, that you've been\Na valiant opponent of fine character.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.35,0:38:24.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我加上这个, 你一直是个\N英勇抗战的出色人物.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.85,0:38:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought the North won\Nthe Civil War?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.91,0:38:27.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是北方\N赢了内战吧，不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.74,0:38:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.79,0:38:46.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.67,0:38:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.74,0:38:49.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.57,0:38:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.66,0:38:50.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.11,0:38:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ben? Ben?\N- Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.18,0:38:56.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 本? 本?\N-爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.78,0:38:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, give him some room.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.87,0:38:58.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 给他点空间.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.68,0:39:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am l?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.74,0:39:00.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.65,0:39:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where am l?\N- Twin Peaks, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.74,0:39:03.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我在哪儿?\N- 双峰镇, 本.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.79,0:39:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l had the strangest dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.87,0:39:10.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了个奇怪的梦.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.46,0:39:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.53,0:39:15.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在梦里.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.13,0:39:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.22,0:39:18.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你也在, 还有你.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.97,0:39:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.05,0:39:21.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太不可思议了.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.27,0:39:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.35,0:39:23.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一场战争.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.71,0:39:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l was General...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.79,0:39:26.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是将军...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.31,0:39:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Robert E. Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.40,0:39:29.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,罗伯特·伊·李将军.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.55,0:39:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And somehow,\Nin spite of incredible odds,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.61,0:39:35.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然而不知怎的,\N尽管在微乎其微的几率下,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.42,0:39:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l won.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.48,0:39:37.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.02,0:39:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're home, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.09,0:39:39.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在回家了, 爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.82,0:39:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.88,0:39:41.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.56,0:39:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l'm home.\N- Attaboy, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.62,0:39:45.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我回家了.\N- 好样的啊, 本.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.96,0:39:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?\NAny, any aftereffects? Dizziness?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.05,0:39:49.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉怎样?\N有任何, 余波? 头昏眼花之类?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.30,0:39:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.35,0:39:53.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉好极了.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.67,0:39:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l feel...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.75,0:39:58.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我感觉...\N- 怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.21,0:40:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What is it, Daddy?\N- What are you doing in those clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.27,0:40:01.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 感觉什么, 爸爸?\N- 你们穿这这些衣服干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.52,0:40:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attaboy, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.57,0:40:09.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好样的, 本.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.52,0:40:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's the joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.62,0:40:11.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 有什么那么好笑的?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.46,0:40:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attaboy, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.53,0:40:15.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好样的, 本.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.40,0:40:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.49,0:40:24.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢做.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.90,0:40:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.97,0:40:27.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且要细致.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.51,0:40:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything must be written\Nwith a steady, uncompromising hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.57,0:40:33.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,每个字都要写的\N沉稳，坚定不移的.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.35,0:40:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.45,0:40:39.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 不, 不.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.22,0:40:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.31,0:40:41.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太吓人了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.12,0:40:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erase.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.18,0:40:43.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,擦掉.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.92,0:40:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erase.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.01,0:40:45.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,擦掉.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.09,0:40:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.19,0:40:51.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.86,0:40:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.93,0:40:53.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.37,0:40:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.45,0:40:59.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.64,0:41:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo, for heaven's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.71,0:41:03.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧, 看在老天爷的份上.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.91,0:41:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.97,0:41:07.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.28,0:41:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.36,0:41:10.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我示范给你看.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.52,0:41:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this:
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.58,0:41:12.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样:
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.75,0:41:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.84,0:41:15.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.09,0:41:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.19,0:41:17.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好多了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.22,0:41:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am proud of you, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.32,0:41:22.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真为你自豪, 里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.77,0:41:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Windom Earle?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.84,0:41:39.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 云顿·厄尔?\N- 是.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.41,0:41:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windom.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.49,0:41:41.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,云顿.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.82,0:41:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty words for pretty girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.88,0:41:47.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好字配美女.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.79,0:41:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one shall be my queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.88,0:41:50.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哪一个会是我的皇后呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.56,0:41:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.62,0:41:53.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,皇后?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.16,0:42:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.23,0:42:01.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不. 不.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.27,0:42:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.36,0:42:02.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.97,0:42:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lick.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.06,0:42:05.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,舔.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.12,0:42:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story rings a little truer\Nwith your fingerprints on--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.19,0:42:20.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有你的指纹在上面的话\N这个故事就显得更真实了--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.62,0:42:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Malcolm, l can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.71,0:42:21.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 马科, 我不能.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.85,0:42:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just your prints.\NLeave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.93,0:42:24.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你的指纹.\N其余的事交给我来办好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.59,0:42:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll do my best to imitate\Nthe actions of a hysteric.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.67,0:42:26.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽量去模仿现场\N歇斯底里的举动.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.02,0:42:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five shots, tightly grouped,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.10,0:42:29.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,5枪, 紧紧集中在一处,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.13,0:42:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as though the gun went off\Nin your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.19,0:42:32.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就像从你这儿\N打出去的一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.20,0:42:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Repeatedly.\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.28,0:42:34.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 连开多枪.\N- 别!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.40,0:42:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! James, James, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.50,0:42:39.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别! 别! 詹姆斯, 詹姆斯, 詹姆斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.17,0:42:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't hurt him any more, please.\N- Give me the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.24,0:42:42.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不要再伤害他了, 求你们了.\N- 给我枪.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.74,0:42:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've called the cops.\NThey're on their way, it won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.85,0:42:45.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经报警了.\N他们已经在路上了, 你们不会得逞的.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.24,0:42:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Malcolm.\N- She's lying. Give me the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.32,0:42:47.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 马科.\N- 她在撒谎. 给我枪.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.21,0:42:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evelyn,\Nplease don't let him die, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.28,0:42:51.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伊夫林,\N求你别让他死啊, 求你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.22,0:42:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Please.\N- Evelyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.32,0:42:53.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 求求你.\N- 伊夫林.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.15,0:42:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the gun, Evelyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.24,0:42:56.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把枪给我, 伊夫林.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.99,0:42:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Evelyn, give me the gun.\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.06,0:42:59.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 伊夫林, 快把枪给我.\N- 不.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.42,0:43:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Evelyn, give me the gun.\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.50,0:43:02.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 伊夫林, 把枪给我.\N- 不.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.43,0:43:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evelyn. Evelyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.50,0:43:05.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伊夫林. 伊夫林.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.86,0:43:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't do this, Malcolm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.93,0:43:08.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我干不出这种事, 马科.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.57,0:43:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then l will.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.67,0:43:10.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我干.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.34,0:43:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.41,0:43:18.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.29,0:43:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.37,0:43:37.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他很生气,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.53,0:43:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.63,0:43:39.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他抓狂了.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.36,0:43:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed Jeffrey,\Ncame back to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.46,0:43:44.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了杰弗里,\N又回来杀我.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.27,0:43:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was ready, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.37,0:43:46.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我早有准备, 尽管如此.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.24,0:43:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got my gun and l shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.33,0:43:51.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是开枪打了他.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.31,0:43:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l shot him till he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.41,0:43:55.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我开枪直到把他打死.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.57,0:44:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.68,0:44:25.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯若琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.72,0:44:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Miss Audrey Horne, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.81,0:44:38.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请转交欧蕊·荷恩小姐.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.76,0:44:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owls?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.85,0:44:40.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,猫头鹰?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.77,0:45:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breathtaking, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.86,0:45:25.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}她很惊艷, 不是吗?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.07,0:45:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A truly beautiful woman, Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.16,0:45:29.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}一个真正的美人, 凯若琳.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.91,0:45:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.99,0:45:31.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}有趣吧?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.51,0:45:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.60,0:45:33.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}经过匹兹堡那次,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.64,0:45:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after all that happened\Nin Pittsburgh,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.73,0:45:37.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}发生了那么多事\N之后,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.28,0:45:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l still love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.38,0:45:40.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我依然爱着她.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.32,0:45:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l know that you do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.42,0:45:43.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我知道你也是.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.52,0:45:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Dale, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.64,0:45:47.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}现在, 戴尔, 小心听好了.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.79,0:45:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.90,0:45:51.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}轮到你走了.{\i0}
